groupDetail.label: Consumer Price Index
groupDetail.description: Includes CPI-trim, CPI-median, and CPI-common as well as other “core” inflation measures.

STATIC_TOTALCPICHANGE.label: Total CPI, Percentage Change over 1 year ago (unadjusted)
STATIC_TOTALCPICHANGE.description: Total CPI, Percentage Change over 1 year ago (unadjusted)

ATOM_V41693242.label: CPIX, Percentage Change over 1 year ago (unadjusted)
ATOM_V41693242.description: The CPI excluding eight of the most volatile components (fruit, vegetables, gasoline, fuel oil, natural gas, mortgage interest, inter-city transportation and tobacco products) as well as the effect of changes in indirect taxes on the remaining components.

STATIC_CPIXFET.label: CPI-XFET, Percentage Change over 1 year ago (unadjusted)
STATIC_CPIXFET.description: The CPI excluding food, energy and the effect of changes in indirect taxes.

CPIW.label: CPIW, Percentage Change over 1 year ago (unadjusted)
CPIW.description: CPIW adjusts each CPI basket weight by a factor that is inversely proportional to the component's variability and is adjusted to exclude the effect of changes in indirect taxes.
